      • handleSave

        public void handleSave​(javafx.event.ActionEvent actionEvent)
                throws java.io.IOException
        Handler for the Add Product Save button. Validates input data from text fields, and sets visible any alerts needed depending on validation results. Upon validation, creates new Product object and adds the object to the Inventory. Increments autoID. Redirects to main form.
        Parameters:
        actionEvent - the event which triggered the method
        Throws:
        java.io.IOException
